    "{\n",
    " \"cells\": [\n",
    "  {\"cell_type\":\"markdown\",\"metadata\":{},\"source\":[\"# FAQ Answer Draft Generator\\n\",\"**NLP Project 54 of 100** — Turn a question bank into answer drafts using templates and LLMs.\"]},\n",
    "  {\"cell_type\":\"code\",\"execution_count\":null,\"metadata\":{},\"outputs\":[],\"source\":[\"import requests, json, pandas as pd\\nimport warnings; warnings.filterwarnings('ignore')\\nprint('Loaded.')\"]},\n",
    "  {\"cell_type\":\"code\",\"execution_count\":null,\"metadata\":{},\"outputs\":[],\"source\":[\"faqs = [\\n    'How do I reset my password?',\\n    'What are your business hours?',\\n    'How do I cancel my subscription?',\\n    'Do you offer refunds?',\\n    'How do I contact support?',\\n    'What payment methods do you accept?',\\n]\\n\\ndef generate_answer(question, model='qwen3:1.7b'):\\n    prompt = f'Write a professional FAQ answer for this question. Keep it under 50 words.\\\\nQuestion: {question} /no_think'\\n    try:\\n        r = requests.post('http://localhost:11434/api/generate',json={'model':model,'prompt':prompt,'stream':False},timeout=60)\\n        return r.json().get('response','')\\n    except:\\n        templates = {'password':'Go to Settings > Security > Reset Password. Follow the email instructions.',\\n                     'hours':'Our business hours are Monday-Friday, 9 AM to 6 PM EST.',\\n                     'cancel':'You can cancel anytime from Settings > Subscription > Cancel.',\\n                     'refund':'We offer full refunds within 30 days of purchase.',\\n                     'contact':'Email support@company.com or use the in-app chat.',\\n                     'payment':'We accept Visa, Mastercard, PayPal, and bank transfers.'}\\n        for k,v in templates.items():\\n            if k in question.lower(): return v\\n        return 'Please contact our support team for assistance.'\\n\\nresults = []\\nfor q in faqs:\\n    a = generate_answer(q)\\n    results.append({'Question': q, 'Answer': a})\\n    print(f'Q: {q}')\\n    print(f'A: {a}\\\\n')\\n\\npd.DataFrame(results)\"]},\n",
    "  {\"cell_type\":\"markdown\",\"metadata\":{},\"source\":[\"## Summary\\n\",\"- **LLMs draft FAQ answers quickly** from questions alone.\\n\",\"- **Template fallback ensures coverage** when LLM is unavailable.\\n\",\"- **Human review is essential** before publishing.\\n\",\"- **Export to CMS/helpdesk** for automated FAQ updates.\"]}\n",
    " ],\n",
